inputs.name: example-ng-tags-spot-3f4b8861
inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 1
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-ng-tags-spot-nodeLaunchConfiguration-d8eb172
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-03711d3b9b21b3a8e","subnet-06e8296c053e2b952","subnet-0fc2dc8f8ba906919","subnet-037f366816336db85"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-tags-cluster2-eksCluster-7aea2dd-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-tags-cluster2-eksCluster-7aea2dd
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: myAutoScalingGroupTag3
                            Value: true
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: k8s.io/cluster-autoscaler/enabled
                            Value: true
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: k8s.io/cluster-autoscaler/example-tags-cluster2-eksCluster-7aea2dd
                            Value: true
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '0'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
